{
  "stem": "24171.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They always accounted every morning--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was always twice-a-day counting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in every camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if-- don't-- in case of something-- somebody was missing from that group, you know, every barrack had their own counting.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if there was not enough, you know, I mean if they made a mistake or something, you could stay there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they said-- in Plaszow, you're staying till-- till-- I don't know how long-- the middle of the night-- till they found out somebody was-- I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they said that they-- the counting does not-- kind of-- in Yiddish, they say, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Weeks,",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A week or so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the first-- the first week was terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's just it hurt, everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you are-- and I couldn't get up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't get up with the headaches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to get up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to get up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no way, no way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to get up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't work there, nothing-- those things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had the-- the-- the diarrhea there took from-- from nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my two nieces-- I had hopes for the father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we know already that whoever went to Auschwitz is gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But their father was, too, in the working camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had two brothers, the one from Prague-- and that I have in the picture-- and Leiser-- [NON-ENGLISH] and Leiser.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were, you know, for the Hungarian-- behind the Hungarian front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were by the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by the Russian border, they sent-- they escaped to Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, they thought that Russia is our friend, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they escaped to Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was one-- a guy from another village, which knew them.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
